                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#333333'>Insight</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#333333'>: </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000'>Kota Palembang</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'> dominates net sales, indicating strong local demand, while other cities present growth opportunities.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
