                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#333333'>Insight</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#333333'>: </run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'>Order volume shows strong fluctuations, with major spikes in </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000'>March</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'> and </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000'>July 2025</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000'> driving overall sales performance.</run>
